in time for its Miami fair. The two big
new features are Art Basel Companion, which =E2=80=9Coffers personalized re=
commendations about where to go and what to see at the show based on user p=
references,=E2=80=9D according to the fair=E2=80=99s release, and Art Basel=
 Lens, which allows users to scan art works to learn more about the artist =
