ont-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">$6.1 million</a></u>. That=E2=80=99s the sam=
e work selling at nearly the same price this season as nine and 12 years ag=
o. Auction house fees eat away at the value, but so does inflation. </li><b=
r/><li><i>About that Koons comeback</i>=E2=80=A6: One of the most interesti=
ng developments this season has been the number of early <b>Jeff Koons</b> =
works on offer. The gambit made sense: The market needs leadership, and pri=
