gh for today. I hope I=E2=80=99ve demonstrated that the overall health of t=
he market is pretty robust, even if the big numbers are not there yet. In f=
act, these sales represent the first step toward the return of those big nu=
mbers. <br/><br/>I=E2=80=99ve got at least one more really good story from =
last week to share with you. I=E2=80=99m hoping we=E2=80=99ll have the righ=
t place for it next week. In the meantime, enjoy your Thanksgiving (for tho=
se of you in the United States, at least).<br/><br/>I=E2=80=99ll speak to y=
ou Sunday as we all prepare for Miami. <br/><br/>Yours,<br/>M<br/></td>
